properties.title: Onboarding Strategy
properties.shortDescription: The Onboarding Strategy template lets DAOs easily expand their onboarding process, customizing the level of permissionlessness, and verifying the actual commitment, knowledge, or skills of new members - in the DAO in general, or in a specific Role.
properties.longDescription: The Onboarding Strategy template lets DAOs easily expand their onboarding process, customizing the level of permissionlessness, and verifying the actual commitment, knowledge, or skills of new members - in the DAO in general, or in a specific Role.
